        "background_color": "#003e52",
        "heading": "How It Works",
        "richtext": "<p>Dr. Jen’s 10% Eggshell Nano Hydroxyapatite Toothpaste uses the natural strength of eggshell-derived nano hydroxyapatite to protect your enamel. With optimal levels of 10% nano-sized hydroxyapatite particles, this premium formula goes beyond traditional hydroxyapatite toothpaste, reducing tooth sensitivity and restoring your smile to its natural brilliance.<br/><br/>Eggshell contains magnesium and zinc, promoting higher calcium absorption. Combined with Xylitol, Dr. Jen's 10% Premium Eggshell nHAp toothpaste supports optimal oral health.</p>",
        "text_color": "#ffffff",
        "full_width_image": "shopify://shop_images/Ritchie_Creative_r1_04R_0226_9a850fcb-93ae-49b0-b46d-15030558f415.jpg",
