            "accordion_answer": "<p>Unlike standard natural toothpastes, we use: </p><ul><li>10% Eggshell-derived hydroxyapatite (the scientifically proven concentration)</li><li>Natural magnesium & zinc for enhanced absorption</li><li>Premium minerals that synthetic versions lack Think of it as nature's perfect formula for your teeth.</li></ul>",
